---
title: Hoisin Turkey Stir Fry with Coconut Rice and Sugar Snap Peas
description: Turkey’s not just Christmas. Super lean and packed with flavour, turkey steaks make a deliciously healthy  addition to tonight’s stir-fry. When we invited our kid taste-tasters to the FreshFarm, they gave this recipe full marks, so we’re sure it will score highly in your kitchen tonight! Add sesame seeds, coconut powder, peanuts and chilli to give this family favourite a more sophisticated twist. Enjoy!
